data.title: Braille Bits
authors: Library - Iowa Department for the Blind
data.meta_description: Listen to Braille Bits on Spotify. Braille Bits is program conducted by the Iowa Library for the Blind and Print Disabled, providing braille lessons online or by mail.  This podcast corresponds with each Braille Bits lesson.  It features each Braille Bits Lesson and an interview with a special guest to discuss all things braille.
